  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      For tough colic resection, evaluation of our practice for these lesions unresectable in
      monoblock and evaluation of the contribution of the hybrid technique EMR (mucosectomy
      dissection) /ESD (submucosal dissection)
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
